<ontology://generated-from-draw-io/mock#Sub-series%20Consists%20Of%20A%20Sketchbook%20Containing%2063%20Watercolours%20And%20Drawings%20Done%20By%20Elizabeth%20Simcoe%20During%20The%20Time%20She%20Accompanied%20Her%20Husband%20To%20Upper%20Canada.%20Many%20Of%20The%20Sketches%20Are%20Rough%20Views%2C%20With%20Few%20Details.%20Some%20Of%20The%20Sketches%20Are%20Identified%20As%20Fort%20Erie%2C%2040%20Mile%20Creek%2C%20Queenston%2C%20Huron%20And%20Chippewa.%20Some%20Of%20The%20Sketches%20Are%20Of%20Flowers%20And%20Have%20Accompanying%20Notes.> a owl:NamedIndividual ;
    rdfs:label "Sub-series consists of a sketchbook containing 63 watercolours and drawings done by Elizabeth Simcoe during the time she accompanied her husband to Upper Canada.  Many of the sketches are rough views, with few details. Some of the sketches are identified as Fort Erie, 40 Mile Creek, Queenston, Huron and Chippewa. Some of the sketches are of flowers and have accompanying notes." .

